
Downgrade the Realtek RTW89 WiFi driver to 6.13.11.

The 6.14 driver has intermittent anomalies.
(1) Remote ssh into the machine may take several seconds.
(2) Discord may take a long time to load or not load at all.

Signed-off-by: Mario Roy <...>


